{"tid":2217990,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（落井下石）月餅抗爭，旁門左道篇","createTime":"2020-09-26T01:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T08:36:58.000Z","uid":70901,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3d833ac83af6e8638a8a7797adc409b5ddb6e69e","tid":2217990,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:30:35.000Z","msg":"係咁的，見好多黃絲話唔買美心藍月餅叫抗爭，但其實你要知對依d黑心商家係零傷害<br />\n<br />\n正道我就唔多講啦，google下大把其他選擇，小弟今曰講嘅係左道<br />\n<br />\n話說肥花dcfever等等二手買賣門票嘅地方都有炒狗放月餅卷，好多係商業送禮d人唔要再放番出黎，有專門收劵人，以前有人專門大量收完賣比支那，可以講係黑市價錢指標，但其實正正係標準市價，因為個價好貼近內部職員買入價位<br />\n<br />\n所以我地唔單止要做死佢地今年價錢，仲要令佢黑市價都跌到仆直，咁下年個黑市價抬唔起頭，正價都要跟住跌<br />\n<br />\n做法好簡單，一人一個fake post, 用低價賣 空頭 月餅，有客問起就話賣左就得，仲要用超低價放卷，好快個黑市價就會跌到100蚊樓下，咁相信連班支那人都會覺得佢只係值100"},{"pid":"f4c7b22ad8050d94bb8a62cfc8848deef53cf175","tid":2217990,"uid":25973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來有咁既玩法"},{"pid":"81627108a5f43e8a78e8506610c34c051b6218a9","tid":2217990,"uid":38932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494d76c40f2b7ab9b36eae0f4d85788465479f5c","tid":2217990,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T02:02:00.000Z","msg":"先推一下"},{"pid":"38939059d22a5b4efa35216c8a75ca1f4060f46f","tid":2217990,"uid":38932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa